### CVE Lookup (NVD)


pip install requests rich


```bash
pip install requests rich
python intel/cve_lookup.py -k apache -n 15
python intel/cve_lookup.py -k openssl --min-cvss 7.0 -n 20
python intel/cve_lookup.py -k wordpress -n 30 --csv-out cves.csv
python intel/cve_lookup.py -k nginx -n 10 --json-out cves.json
